About Me


I am Executive Committee Member at IEEE Students' Branch, VIT Pune



I am an engineering student at Vishwakarma Institute Of Technology, Pune. I study in the AI-DS branch. I love Machine Learning, artificial intelligence and web development. I am a Linux enthusiast and like to keep Fedora as my main machine. I am a security and privacy enthusiast too.
